value.title: Walmart, Disney suspend contributions to U.S. lawmakers who opposed Biden certification

value.title: Trump's top bankers Deutsche Banks and Signature cut future ties
value.excerpt: In the wake of the deadly riots on Capitol Hill last week, Deutsche Bank and Signature Bank have said they are cutting future ties with President Donald Trump.
